text: Elizaveta Rutkovskaja (born 9 December 1997) is an Estonian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Estonia women's national team. ==Career== Rutkovskaja has been capped for the Estonia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian women's footballers Category:Estonia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Estonian people of Russian descent
